ing: 2 (16 ounce) packages hot dogs, cut into pieces
des: "This is great for B-day parties, last minute dinner, Christmas, any occasion, the guys especially like it for superbowl! BIG KID PLEASER!  Easy, quick, and you usually have all ingredients in your home. You wont be disappointed!"
ins: Place hot dog pieces, pineapple, brown sugar, white sugar and baked beans into a slow cooker. Cook on high for 15 minutes, turn down to low, and let simmer for another 15 minutes, or until ready to serve. This dish can be kept on low all day.
